\\/p>\\n\",\"<p>Straw man<\\/p>\\n\"]},{\"subContentId\":\"50ebf660-b87d-4db2-a10d-b2552c1544da\",\"question\":\"<p>It\\u2019s simple: &nbsp;either we are a freedom-loving campus or we aren\\u2019t? &nbsp;I choose freedom, and I believe all of America\\u2019s veterans would agree with me.&nbsp;Perhaps the Chancellor has an ulterior motive for instituting the ban and is using smokers as a scapegoat. <\\/p>\\n\",\"answers\":[\"<p>Ad hominem <\\/p>\\n\",\"<p>Hasty generalization<\\/p>\\n\",\"<p>Slippery Slope<\\/p>\\n\",\"<p>No fallacy.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\"]}],\"behaviour\":{\"timeoutCorrect\":2000,\"timeoutWrong\":3000,\"soundEffectsEnabled\":false,\"enableRetry\":true,\"enableSolutionsButton\":true,\"passPercentage\":100},\"l10n\":{\"resultSlideTitle\":\"You got :numcorrect of :maxscore correct\",\"showSolutionButtonLabel\":\"Show solution\",\"retryButtonLabel\":\"Retry\",\"solutionViewTitle\":\"Solution\",\"correctText\":\"Correct!\",\"incorrectText\":\"Incorrect!\",\"muteButtonLabel\":\"Mute feedback sound\",\"closeButtonLabel\":\"Close\",\"slideOfTotal\":\"Slide :num of :total\"}}','evaluate-logical-fallacies','div',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(7,'2017-05-10 02:02:12','2017-05-10 02:02:23',1,'Mark the Words: BEAM',4,'{\"checkAnswerButton\":\"Check\",\"tryAgainButton\":\"Retry\",\"showSolutionButton\":\"Show solution\",\"score\":\"You got @score of @total points\",\"behaviour\":{\"enableRetry\":true,\"enableSolutionsButton\":true},\"correctAnswer\":\"Correct!\",\"incorrectAnswer\":\"Try again!\",\"missedAnswer\":\"Missed!\",\"displaySolutionDescription\":\"Task is updated to contain the solution.\",\"textField\":\"<p><em>Provides an overview or puts the topic in context.&nbsp;</em></p>\\n\\n<p>*Background*<br>\\nExhibit<br>\\nArgument<br>\\nMethod</p>\\n\\n<p><em>Provides another writer\'s analysis of your topic</em></p>\\n\\n<p>Background<br>\\nExhibit<br>\\n*Argument*<br>\\nMethod</p>\\n\\n<p><em>Primarily used to back up your claims.</em></p>\\n\\n<p>Background<br>\