id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"https://pressbooks.com/?p=4486\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:430:\"What is EPUB3 and do I need it? Should I change old ebook files to this new format? EPUB3 is the new format of EPUB. In general if you&#8217;re not doing anything complicated, you won&#8217;t really notice a difference&#8211;you could use either EPUB2 or EPUB3. EPUB3 is backwards compatible to EPUB2, so it should be <p class=\"read-more\"> <a href=\"https://pressbooks.com/blog/ebook-formatting-answers-epub3/\">more &#8594;</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"Liz\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1304:\"<h2><a href=\"https://pressbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ebook-3-sm.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-4541\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4541\" src=\"https://pressbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ebook-3-sm.jpg\" alt=\"Woman Reading Ebook\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"https://pressbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ebook-3-sm.jpg 700w, https://pressbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ebook-3-sm-300x200.jpg 300w, https://pressbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ebook-3-sm-480x320.jpg 480w, https://pressbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ebook-3-sm-65x43.jpg 65w, https://pressbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ebook-3-sm-225x150.jpg 225w, https://pressbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ebook-3-sm-350x234.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></h2>\r\n<p>What is EPUB3 and do I need it? Should I change old ebook files to this new format? EPUB3 is the new format of EPUB. In general if you’re not doing anything complicated, you won’t really notice a difference–you could use either EPUB2 or EPUB3. EPUB3 is backwards compatible to EPUB2, so it should be compatible to old readers. There’s no reason you need to switch–in...</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://pressbooks.com/blog/ebook-formatting-answers-epub3/\" rel=\"external nofollow\">Source</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:32;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"Ebook Formatting Answers: Submitting a MOBI File vs. a Word File to Amazon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://pressbooks.com/blog/ebook-formatting-answers-submitting-mobi-vs-word-files-to-amazon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 14 Mar 2016 18:45:58 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Book Formatting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"https://pressbooks.com/?p=4443\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:432:\"Why would I want to create a MOBI file using Pressbooks if Amazon 