{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Hugh\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:490:\"<p>We’ve just added a couple of new book themes for PressBooks, still in the “traditional” vein. We’ll be adding some funkier designs in the fall. In the mean time, let us introduce you to Austen and Fitzgerald. Austen Theme The Austen theme is named after Jane Austen, and it’s a classic all-serif font book design, built for novels, memoirs and straight text.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://pressbooks.com/blog/new-themes-fitzgerald-and-austen/\" rel=\"external nofollow\">Source</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:231;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"Privacy Settings, Catalog Page, Open Access\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:132:\"https://pressbooks.com/blog/pressbooks-july-news-book-home-page-privacy-settings-catalog-page-events-some-cool-open-access-projects/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 15 Jul 2013 14:43:16 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Pressbooks Features & Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"http://blog.pressbooks.com/?p=432\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:536:\"Hello and Happy July, Have you written any great books lately? We hope so, and we&#8217;re always trying to make PressBooks a better platform for publishing those great books. In this quick Newsletter you&#8217;ll find some new features, and a couple of interesting Open Access projects, from Duke University Press, and University of Minnesota Press. <p class=\"read-more\"> <a href=\"https://pressbooks.com/blog/pressbooks-july-news-book-home-page-privacy-settings-catalog-page-events-some-cool-open-access-projects/\">more &#8594;</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Hugh\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:584:\"<p>Hello and Happy July, Have you written any great books lately? We hope so, and we’re always trying to make PressBooks a better platform for publishing those great books. In this quick Newsletter you’ll find some new features, and a couple of interesting Open Access projects, from Duke University Press, and University of Minnesota Press. Contents: New Book Home Page Privacy Settings...</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://pressbooks.com/blog/pressbooks-july-news-book-home-page-privacy-settings-catalog-page-events-some-cool-open-access-projects/\" rel=\"external nofollow\">Source</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:232;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0: