f America’s veterans would agree with me. Perhaps the Chancellor has an ulterior motive for instituting the ban and is using smokers as a scapegoat.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nEach question below will show you a section from the passage. Decide which logical fallacy best applies to the statement, or select \"no fallacy.\"\r\n\r\n[h5p id=\"6\"]','Evaluating logical fallacies','','inherit','closed','closed','','39-revision-v1','','','2017-05-09 19:56:32','2017-05-09 19:56:32','',39,'http://localhost/writ101/2017/05/09/39-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(44,1,'2017-05-09 20:10:02','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2017-05-09 20:10:02','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/writ101/?post_type=chapter&p=44',0,'chapter','',0),(45,1,'2017-05-09 20:10:17','2017-05-09 20:10:17','','Source Integration','','publish','closed','closed','','integrating-material-from-sources','','','2017-05-09 20:21:46','2017-05-09 20:21:46','',0,'http://localhost/writ101/?post_type=part&#038;p=45',3,'part','',0),(46,1,'2017-05-09 20:10:44','2017-05-09 20:10:44','<h2>Why is it important to understand how to integrate sources into your own writing?</h2>\r\nWriters use sources to support and develop their own ideas.  Learning how to integrate sources successfully is important for several reasons:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Well-integrated sources build the strength of an argument.</li>\r\n 	<li>Well-integrated sources enhance credibility for the writer.</li>\r\n 	<li>Well-integrated sources contribute to readability.</li>\r\n 	<li>Well-integrated sources demonstrate precision of thought and language choice.</li>\r\n</ul>','Why it matters: Source Integration','','publish','closed','closed','','why-it-matters-integrating-material-from-sources','','','2017-05-09 20:29:46','2017-05-09 20:29:46','',45,'http://localhost/writ101/?post_type=chapter&#038;p=46',5,'chapter','',0),(47,1,'2017-05-09 20:10:44','2017-05-09 20:10:44','','Why it matters: Integrating Material from Sources','','inherit','closed','closed','','46-revision-v1','','','2017-05-09 20:10:44','2017-05-09 20:10:44','',46,'http://localhost/writ101/2017/05/09/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(48,1,'2017-05-09 20:29:40','2017-05-09 20:29:40','<h2>Why is it important to understand how to integrate sources into your own writing?</h2>\nWriters use sources to support and develop their own ideas.  Learning how to integrate sources successfully is important for several reasons:\n<ul>\n 	<li>\nWell-integrated sources build the strength of an argument.\nWell-integrated sources enhance credibility for the writer.\nWell-integrated sources contribute to readability.\nWell-integrated sources demonstrate precision of thought and language choice.</li>\n</ul>','Why it matters: Source Integration','','inherit','closed','closed','','46-autosave-v1','','','2017-05-09 20:29:40','2017-05-09 20:29:40','',46,'http://localhost/writ101/2017/05/09/46-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(49,1,'2017-05-09 20:21:32','2017-05-09 20:21:32','','Integrating Material from Sources','','publish','closed','closed','','integrating-material-from-sources','','','2017-05-09 20:21:32','2017-05-09 20:21:32','',45,'http://localhost/writ101/?post_type=chapter&#038;p=49',6,'chapter','',0),(50,1,'2017-05-09 20:21:32','2017-05-09 20:21:32','','Integrating Material from Sources','','inherit','closed','closed','','49-revision-v1','','','2017-05-09 20:21:32','2017-05-09 20:21:32','',49,'http://localhost/writ101/2017/05/09/49-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(51,1,'2017-05-09 20:26:50','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Book Info','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2017-05-09 20:26:50','2017-05-09 20:26:50','',0,'http://localhost/writ101/?post_type=metadata&#038;p=51',0,'metadata','',0),(52,1,'2017-05-09 20:29:46','2017-05-09 20:29:46','<h2>Why is it important to understand how to integrate sources into your own writing?</h2>\r\nWriters use sources to support and develop their own ideas.  Learning how to integrate sources successfully is important for several reasons:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Well-integrated sources build the strength of an argument.</li>\r\n 	<li>Well-integrated sources enhance credibility for the writer.</li>\r\n 	<li>Well-integrated sources contribute to readability.</li>\r\n 	<li>Well-integrated sources demonstrate precision of thought and language choice.</li>\r\n</ul>','Why it matters: Source Integration','','inherit','closed','closed','','46-revision-v1','','','2017-05-09 20:29:46','2017-05-09 20:29:46','',46,'http://localhost/writ101/2017/05/09/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
